comments: Murray (DEN) makes marginal contact with Embiid (PHI) as Embiid is retrieving the pass.
Embiid (PHI) initiates contact with his elbow and hooks Murray (DEN) dislodging Murray from his legally obtained defensive position.
Richardson (PHI) cleanly deflects the pass being thrown to Murray (DEN) cleanly stealing the ball.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Replay review of the foul called on Embiid (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Embiid makes contact with Millsap that affects his SQBR.
Harris (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Barton (DEN).
Millsap (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Embiid (PHI).
Embiid (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Murray (DEN).
As Millsap (DEN) is retrieving the pass, Richardson (PHI) makes marginal contact with Millsap as Millsap is able to gather the ball and maintain possession.
As Millsap (DEN) is dribbling out of the post, Embiid (PHI) takes a clean swipe at the ball as Millsap loses control of the ball on his own.
As Millsap (DEN) begins to gather the ball, Richardson (PHI) makes marginal contact with Millsap allowing Millsap to gather the ball and pass.
Richardson (PHI) makes incidental high-five contact with Jokic (DEN) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Barton (DEN) makes a natural move to get open as he does not extend his arms into Harris (PHI) and push off.

During the inbound, Jokic (DEN) places his hand to the opposite side of Embiid's (PHI) hip and brings his hand to a pause. As Jokic releases his hand from Embii's hip, he grasps Embiid's jersey and affects his FOM.  A personal foul should be called instead of an offensive foul.
Horford (PHI) commits a take foul on Barton (DEN).
